```csharp
private static bool ProcessPayment(decimal amount)
{
    if (amount <= 0) throw new ArgumentException("Amount must be positive");
    return true;
}
```

The test host will **automatically detect** your change and re-run the test — no rebuild needed. Repeat until it passes, then **Ctrl+C** and run `dotnet test` for a final full build confirmation.

